{"tid":1454774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我警告你班廢青唔好搞機場D後勤設備","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:35:39.000Z","uid":282325,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c21d85dbda91702deed188c47441317a219d87d","tid":1454774,"uid":282325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">客機呢D大型飛行器好撚化學架<br />\n少咁個parts都唔飛得<br />\n冇燃料又唔飛得<br />\n仲有機上d供餐呀俾毒氣掂到仲點食？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咪亂搞呀屌你地班死廢青，一陣搞撚到幾日都飛唔撚到我再叫多D福建同鄉落黎招呼你地<br />\n<br />\n支持香港警察嚴正執法，放多D催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260efa492a23ec1d31e68ea97a071fe7fee2d87d","tid":1454774,"uid":282325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"屌你地班死廢青阻人返工"},{"pid":"59ce81bb4154bba39a08c2a827254d980f966176","tid":1454774,"uid":282325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"屌你地班死廢青阻人返工"},{"pid":"1c5e11a2e8105178b0732cd36367f817f52da3d0","tid":1454774,"uid":282325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:19:59.000Z","msg":"屌你地班死廢青阻人返工"},{"pid":"910e92d5d33a767f3de1a62263da550792e263cf","tid":1454774,"uid":282325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"屌你地班死廢青阻人返工"},{"pid":"38f2a1abdc53f11306dbd005985dfee8004b5cca","tid":1454774,"uid":282325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"屌你地班死廢青阻人返工"},{"pid":"af0c9a5f150f3